snippet.textDisplay:
A Nazrul Geeti finally!! ♥ 
Ritu Raj has sung it so beautifully. There's something in his voice.

I was thinking in the end credit we will hear "Esho He Boishakh" since today is Pahela Boishakh but it didn't happen. It will be great to hear a mash up of "O Mon Ramazan er Oi Rozar Seshe" on Eid day with any other song. 

BTW we want more Nazrul Geeti on Coke Studio. 

Bagichay Bulbuli Tui Ful Shakha Te Dish Ne Aji Dol... 
Ajo Tar Ful Kolider Ghum Tuteni Tondrate Bilol...🎵

I'm totally in love with this song. ♥
